alt: A gold-colored plastic trophy of a runner is held in someone's left hand. The label on the statue says 'WINNER'.
People are eating at a dining room table. One person is standing on a chair, holding a trophy and giving a speech.
A group of sweaty people stand on the front porch of a house smiling and full of happy wishes for the birthday boy.
Two sweaty dudes race to wrap presents while wearing large latex gloves.

A handwritten poem that says: 'There resides a Scott on South Candler, / A stunning athletic running rambler. / His calvese are so bouldery, / They exhaust all his hosiery. / I hope he gets a birthday sock sampler! / / Brent!'
A gold-colored plastic trophy is dressed in a festive costume of pipe cleaners.
A group of about 20 people assemble outside on the sidewalk for the start of a race.
4 people pose for a picture. 2 are pointing to the woman in front.
A child cheeses for the camera while holding a glass of orange juice.
Two grown men compare their calves. One of the men's calves are gigantic. The other's are slender.
A figurine sits on a table with its head broken off and sitting next to the body.
A figurine sits on a table next to a small bottle of Gorilla Glue.
